PLEASE SEED AFTER YOU'VE DOWNLOADED!

I've been sharing AC 2.0 files that I pay a membership for so the least you can do is seed them after downloading. I'm not going to bear the burden and share more files like these if people don't seed. I uploaded this file 4 hours ago and so far my ratio is almost 6. It's been uploaded to 8 users already, yet I'm the only one still seeding. PLEASE SEED. Keep the community strong. Thanks.
